FBIS4-62876 "drsov097_p_94008" FBIS-SOV-94-097 Daily Report 18 May 1994 CAUCASUS Armenia Border Trade With Iran To Begin 11 Jun Border Trade With Iran To Begin 11 Jun NC1905064094 Yerevan SNARK in English 1454 GMT 18 May 94 NC1905064094 Yerevan SNARK English BFN [Text] Yerevan 18 May (SNARK)--Border trade between Armenia and Iran will begin since June 11. The Armenian President's Press-Service told SNARK such agreement had been reached during a meeting between representatives of two states. There were also discussed questions of simplifying the border crossing regime, intensifying the building of the bridge over Araks border river and regulation of the customs problems. The head of the Armenian delegation Gagik Garutunyan got acquainted with the course of the bridge's building and viewed the place, intended for the border trade.
